transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ha, Himal bhai bol raha hu mai Khushi Industries se.
Customer: Kaha se?
Executive: Khushi Industries Navsari Gujarat.
Customer: Hanji sir.
Executive: Mera catalog manager kaun hai uska mere ko number chahiye urgent mein.
Customer: Catalog number ek second aap rukiyega mai dekhti hu.






















































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































Hello
Customer: Mai number bol rahi hu aap aur number likh lijiye.
Executive: Ha boliye.
Customer: Ek minute.

Executive: 85271
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: 29270
Customer: Naam kya hai?
Customer: Abhishek.
Executive: Abhishek to wo catalog manager nahi hai wo to faltu ki baat kar raha hai mere ko uske upar ka number chahiye.
Customer: Sir to aap mujhe bataye kya concern hai mai ek bari usko relate kar deti hu kyuki abhi lunch time hai aap 3 baje aap call kar lijiye.
Executive: To mai owner ko phone lagau kya seedha?
Customer: Kya sir?
Executive: Owner ko phone lagau kya mai abhi?
Executive: Isi number pe call back kijiyega jisse aapne call kiya hai mai baat karwa dungi aapki.
Customer: Madam satisfaction nahi mil raha hai mere ko sir iska aapka maine ek lakh rupees ka TrustSeal package liya hai. Mai aapko legal mein dal dunga mai seedha seedha court case dal dunga mai agar mere ko satisfaction answer nahi mila to ya to fir mai isko phone karta hu. 3 baje call kariega mai baat kara dungi mai mana thodi kar rahi hu aapki baat karane se.
Customer: Aapke time pe sab log free rehte hai kya?
Customer: Abhi abhi abhi fir se baat kiya tha wo kaisi baat kar raha hai mere sath hum log kya kar sakte hai to iske liye hi bithaya hua hai aap log to hum log kya kar sakte hai. Sir do se teen ka lunch time hota hai mai is time kuch bhi nahi kar sakti kyuki mai desktop pe nahi hu agar mere pass hota to mai dekh ke bata deti.

Executive: Thik hai mai aapko owner
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer wants catalog manager number.

- Customer is not satisfied with service.

- Customer threatens to take legal action.



Resolution:

- Executive provided catalog manager number.

- Executive asked to call at 3 PM.

- Executive assured to connect with senior.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will call back at 3 PM.



Alert (If Any):

- complaint

- escalation

- legal
